reviews.text: So many different choice on food, price is really good, my kids love this restaurant very much!
low price and quality is good.
Very affordable pizza, spaghetti, steak, salad and a lot of varieties to choose from.

The food here is good and cheap,  but 
- the seats are not arranged well, not comfortable and hard to go in and out 
- the service is so bad, the servers are so impolite, not verbally,  but the temper and the way they treat you 
-  the queue management is not good, elderly have to stand and wait without any seats offer

Budget chain Italian restaurant with many branches in Hong Kong.
As would expect from this chain, cheap and good value food.  Though the service is not quite as prompt as experienced in other branches.

result.name: 薩莉亞

reviews.text: So many different choice on food, price is really good, my kids love this restaurant very much!
味道ok,價錢平，但超多甲甴😱

離我屋企近，這裡的莎莉亞可看風景，我喜歡這裡的環境！還有就是杯子是隔熱的，裝熱水不怕被燙。辣味雞翅最最最讚了，忌簾玉米湯，雞肉多利亞，水牛芝士薄餅，波羅煙肉薄餅，雞塊，番茄海鮮意麵，松露菌菇意麵，招牌溫泉蛋煙肉意麵真的都特別的好吃，我經常去都是點這些，而且不貴，就30蚊左右。兩個人去也就100蚊左右就可以吃飽。有時人多需要排隊拿號，但是效率很快，很快就可以進去，送餐速度也快。唯一覺得不足的就是番茄水牛味道很奇怪啊，有一次點了，番茄吃完了，水牛怎麼都吃不下！
大集團食物中規中矩 可惜 嗰次我去到 有少少不愉快經歷 就係 畀人冷對待
9号去王大仙商埸分店,吃了西兰花吾新鮮好毅,芝士石禍饭勁漏,克松露鸡粉好咸.全都难吃

reviews.text: It is fun to walk around. The air condition is sufficient here. You may find variety of stores. There is a large super market on the underground.

It was a good place for ppl having dogs.
As they allow the dogs to walk in the shopping mall.
Also, you could also borrow the pet trolley to shop around, which is very convenient👍🏻

A nice shopping mall in San Po Kong which provides a lot of shops, supermarket and restaurants.  However, it is located near an industrial area and can not be reached by Mass Transit Railway.  But, you can reach there by buses, there are plenty of buses passing by and stop right in front of the mall.  Indeed,  driving your own car is the most convenience way to go there as there is a large parking lot with plenty of parking spaces. And, free parking will be offered if you spend a specified amount of money there.

Mikiki shopping mall, superstore and restaurants. 
Located at 638 Prince  Edward Road, San Po Kong. Kowloon.
Please like my review if its helpful. 🙏

Heartful Veggie is good for health food, The menu more  and more different choices for customers. For example : sushi,  soup, rice and other vegetables. So you want to go to the this place. I think the place is best choice.👍👍👏
